abstract: Viktor Troicki defeats Mikhail Kukushkin to win Sydney International tennis tournament.
lead_paragraph: Viktor Troicki of Serbia beat Kazakhstan’s Mikhail Kukushkin, 6-2, 6-3, to win the Sydney International title in the first ATP final between two qualifiers.
snippet: Viktor Troicki of Serbia beat Kazakhstan’s Mikhail Kukushkin, 6-2, 6-3, to win the Sydney International title in the first ATP final between two qualifiers.

headline.main: Serbian Defeats Fellow Qualifier to Win Sydney International Title
